LircChannelChanger

LircChannelChanger is a perl script intended for use with the
MythTV (http://www.mythtv.org) open source DVR project.  It
providers an external channel changing script using LIRC
(http://www.lirc.org) the Linux Infrared Remote Control programs.

LircChannelChanger supports a large number of options in order
to handle a signficant subset of the requirements of those that
need an external channel changing script using LIRC.

Development and testing has been performed only on Linux.
